highlights.text: “Closer” by The Chainsmokers and Halsey has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 82 weeks straight.
Drake has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “In My Feelings” is the highest at #1.
“God is a woman” by Ariana Grande is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Summertime Magic” by Childish Gambino is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 169 spots at #22.
